      "duration": 4710,
      "text": "In the middle of one of the\nsongs, during Miles' solo,"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 4910,
      "endTime": 13590,
      "duration": 8680,
      "text": "I played this chord that was\nso wrong I thought I had just"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 13590,
      "endTime": 18150,
      "duration": 4560,
      "text": "destroyed everything, and\nreduced that great night"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 18150,
      "endTime": 19320,
      "duration": 1170,
      "text": "to rubble."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 19320,
      "endTime": 25130,
      "duration": 5810,
      "text": "Miles took a breath, and\nhe played some notes."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 25130,
      "endTime": 26520,
      "duration": 1390,
      "text": "And he made my chord right."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 29780,
      "endTime": 33940,
      "duration": 4160,
      "text": "And I could not figure\nout how he did that."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 33940,
      "endTime": 36410,
      "duration": 2470,
      "text": "It sounded like magic, you know?"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 36410,
      "endTime": 40185,
      "duration": 3775,
      "text": "It took me years to figure\nout what actually happened."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 40185,
      "endTime": 41060,
      "duration": 875,
      "text": "Here's what happened."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 44550,
      "endTime": 47820,
      "duration": 3270,
      "text": "I judged what I had played."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 47820,
      "endTime": 49920,
      "duration": 2100,
      "text": "Miles didn't."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 49920,
      "endTime": 54680,
      "duration": 4760,
      "text": "Miles just accepted it as\nsomething new that happened."
    },
    {
      "startTime": 54680,
      "endTime": 59770,
      "duration": 5090,
      "text": "And he did what any jazz\nmusician should always"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 59770,
      "endTime": 64840,
      "duration": 5070,
      "text": "try to do, and that is try\nto make anything that happens"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 64840,
      "endTime": 69010,
      "duration": 4170,
      "text": "into something of value."
